<nav class="navbar navbar-fixed-top navbar-default header landing-header">
	<div class="main-logo">
		<span class="logo-glyph"></span><span class="logo-type">Coilbee</span>
	</div>
</nav>
<div class="row main-jumbotron">
	<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
		<div class="col-sm-7">
			<h1 class="jumbotron-text">Discover, create and share thematic link directories</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-5 jumbotron-image-wrapper">
			<%= image_tag("jumbotron.jpg", class: "jumbotron-image", alt: "Link Directory") %>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row landing-account">
	<div class="signup-block">
		<%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, :class => 'btn btn-success signup-btn landing', id: "signup-btn" %>
		<div id="signup">
			<div class="landing-panel">
				<%= render 'devise/registrations/new' %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="login-block">
		<span class="login-text">Already have an account?</span>
		<%= link_to "Login", new_user_session_path, :class => 'btn login-btn landing', id: "login-btn" %>
		<div id="login">
			<div class="landing-panel">
				<%= render 'devise/sessions/new' %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row landing-description-wrapper">
	<div class="col-md-4 landing-description">
		<div class="image desc-img-1"></div>
		<h2>Organize Directories</h2>
		<p>Collect all your links to resources, videos, books and articles in a categorized directory. Give each link its place inside categories and sections. Tag the entries to quickly search and group them. Start creating your own personalized directory or contribute to existing ones!</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4 landing-description">
		<div class="image desc-img-2"></div>
		<h2>Learn</h2>
		<p>Quickly become informed and proficient in any subject. Following the semantic organization of links you can obtain knowledge about a specific field or easily access useful resources. Use the group filter to choose your preferred type of learning or see entries from a specific geographic area.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-4 landing-description">
		<div class="image desc-img-3"></div>
		<h2>Share Link Directories</h2>
		<p>Collaborate with co-workers, classmates or friends by sharing directories of interest. Assign moderators to the libraries you created to have them help you maintain and expand the repository. Make your directories public to share with the world the organized knowledge you created.</p>
	</div>
</div>

